testExecuteProposal().details: Uses vm.warp to simulate the passage of time until the execution period is available

testContribution().notice: Should correctly calculate each investor's balance and the total DAO balance after contributions

testContributionFailsWhenInsufficientFun.notice: Should fail because the investor attempts to contribute 0 ethers

testContributionFailsWhenPeriodEnded().notice: Should fail because the contribution is made after the contribution period has ended

testCreateProposal().notice: Should create a proposal and ensure that the values are correctly stored

testCreateProposalFailsWhenInsufficientD.notice: Should fail because the DAO contract does not have enough Ether to fund the proposal

testExecuteProposal().notice: Should transfer the correct amount of Ether to the proposal recipient after a successful vote and execution

testExecuteProposalFailsWhenQuorumNotMet.notice: Should fail because the quorum was not met (not enough votes were cast)

testExecuteProposalFailsWhenVotingPeriod.notice: Should fail because the voting period has not ended yet

testExecuteProposalWhenInsufficientDAOFu.notice: Should fail because the DAO does not have sufficient funds to execute the proposal

testInitFailsWhenNotOwner().notice: Should fail because the caller of initializeDAO is not the owner

testRedeemShare().notice: Should correctly update the investor's balance and DAO balance after redemption

testRedeemShareFailsWhenInsufficientAmou.notice: Should fail because the DAO does not have enough Ether to fulfill the redemption request

testRedeemShareFailsWhenInsufficientFund.notice: Should fail because the investor attempts to redeem more Ether than they have deposited

testTransferShare().notice: Should correctly transfer shares between investors and update their balances

testTransferShareFailsWhenInsufficientAm.notice: Should fail because the investor attempts to transfer zero shares

testTransferShareFailsWhenInsufficientSh.notice: Should fail because the investor attempts to transfer more shares than they have

testTransferShareFailsWhenTransferringTo.notice: Should fail because the investor attempts to transfer shares to themselves

testVoteProposal().notice: Should correctly update the vote count after a successful vote

testVoteProposalFailsWhenAlreadyVoted().notice: Should fail because the investor has already voted on this proposal

testVoteProposalFailsWhenNotInvestor().notice: Should fail because the caller is not a DAO investor

testVoteProposalFailsWhenVotingPeriodEnd.notice: Should fail because the voting period has ended
